#What is the heap memory ?
The heap memory is used to store Java Object.

#-Xms<size> - to set the minimal/starting Java heap size
#-Xmx<size> - to set the maximum Java heap size
#-XX:MaxPermSize - to set the maximum size of the permanent generation
set JVM_ARGS="-Xms200m -Xmx512m -Dpropname=propvalue..."
